"Alternatively, to load the driver as a module at boot time, place the\n"
"following line in man:loader.conf[5]:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/kernelconfig/_index.adoc:105
#, no-wrap
